    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior and interior show some light signs of use consistent with its age, such as minor surface scratches and slight upholstery wear, it remains a clean and presentable car. It is a solid, reliable vehicle that offers a great balance of performance and value.",
      "price": 34000.0,
